(ns farsund.market.events
  (:require [re-frame.core :as rf]
            [taoensso.timbre :as timbre]))


(rf/reg-event-fx
  :data/get-market-report
  (fn [{db :db} _]
    {:ws/send {:event      :data/market-report
               :on-success [:data/get-market-report.success]
               :on-failure [:data/get-market-report.failure]}}))


(rf/reg-event-fx
  :data/get-market-report.success
  (fn [{db :db} [_ {:keys [data]}]]
    {:db (assoc-in db [:data :market-report] data)}))


(rf/reg-event-fx
  :data/get-market-report.failure
  (fn [{db :db} [_ {:keys [data]}]]
    (timbre/error :data/get-market-report.failure)))
